1. Practise yoga everyday! 🧘🏻‍♀️ A handstand a day keeps the stress and boredom away 🤸🏻‍♀️
2. Spend time with my family at home! Although we are all at home together, my dearest mother will take the effort to ensure we spend quality time actually talking to each other and doing things  TOGETHER, such as playing mahjong at home (non gambling version), having movie nights and also doing Gong meditation/HIIT together hehe yay
3. Online shopping!! Shopping is self care and self love ❤️ even though the shops are closed, there are now lotsa boutiques which offer virtual styling and deliver clothes and bags for try on purposes amidst the circuit breaker times. It is so important to neglect the very loved ones who are by your side so every effort should be made to show each other how we care!!!
